    {
      "turn_id": 3,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "地址无效直接返回错误，没有重试。校验通过后，先PrepareTransaction准备交易数据，再SignTransaction用私钥签名，这两个步骤必须解耦，方便后续接入硬件钱包。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "ErrorInvalidAddress",
        "PrepareTransaction",
        "SignTransaction"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 4,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "好的，我先搭建主骨架：Start节点出发，经过Receive Request触发地址校验CheckAddress，然后分出Yes/No两条支路。",
